{"tid":752841,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"水果要點食先最健康?","createTime":"2018-07-23T06:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T10:24:35.000Z","uid":195337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9290846f54b4faf1f7c74414bea5d94c4a7d1649","tid":752841,"uid":195337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"上網睇有啲人話果糖都會令人肥所以水果唔可以食得太多<br />\n因為網上有太多不同嘅資訊, 所以想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果一個成人一日大概應該食幾多份水果, 同咩時候食係最好?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d436c95a2e2f1d95e72a157f28c90498565466","tid":752841,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"咩生果都食，唔好揀。同埋唔好炸汁飲，要食原個"},{"pid":"1c1ccba8899ca04364aa9a5ff80794a701c5682e","tid":752841,"uid":195438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"吃完整嘅水果其實無事<br />\n同牛奶嘅乳糖一樣<br />\n因為佢地唔係游離糖"},{"pid":"2aaea524b9773950b1245d5e610d8dc2a1d648e5","tid":752841,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d436c95a2e2f1d95e72a157f28c90498565466","tid":752841,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"咩生果都食，唔好揀。同埋唔好炸汁飲，要食原個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"炸汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5953993c8f9dc897ee4f4ed8baf86702dc4cdc","tid":752841,"uid":195438,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"精製食物不嬲易吸收易肥<br />\n例如白米<br />\n如果你打做果汁其實就係精製<br />\n所以點解食水果要食完整一個"},{"pid":"3e495f4449ccf83b72dc570da6eb7c8dc4f194a7","tid":752841,"uid":195337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c1ccba8899ca04364aa9